                        <interp inst="t18390708-name-315" type="given" value="HENRY"></interp>HENRY SOUTHAM</persName>
                  </hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> This property was in the shop the night before.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">BORRITT</hi>—<hi rend="largeCaps">
                     <rs id="t18390708-2057-verdict-1" type="verdictDescription">
