                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-2057-18390708 t18390708-2057-punishment-47"></join>Transported for Fifteen Years</rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">STAPLETON</hi>, <hi rend="largeCaps">STRONG</hi>, and <hi rend="largeCaps">WISEMAN</hi>—<hi rend="largeCaps">
